293
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:17,027
<i>Virtual colonoscopy was clean.</i>

294
00:18:17,096 --> 00:18:19,156
No colon cancer.

295
00:18:19,231 --> 00:18:21,410
What happened to our regular,
