299
00:18:32,878 --> 00:18:37,043
But not of tests. Just
embarrassing ones.

300
00:18:37,116 --> 00:18:38,846
Yeah.

301
00:18:42,989 --> 00:18:47,689
It's not an inflammatory process. It's
not a clot, because Chase's angio says so.

302
00:18:48,761 --> 00:18:52,391
And it's not cancer,
because her tush is perfect.

303
00:18:52,465 --> 00:18:56,300
Anybody else got an Aunt
Elyssa with weird stuff?

304
00:18:58,437 --> 00:19:00,736
<i>Maybe it's worth looking into—</i>

305
00:19:00,806 --> 00:19:03,037
I thought you said
Carly's angio was clean.

306
00:19:03,109 --> 00:19:06,546
It was clean.

307
00:19:13,953 --> 00:19:15,888
You guys see the problem here?

308
00:19:18,057 --> 00:19:21,186
There's no indication
of any abnormalities.

309
00:19:21,260 --> 00:19:23,195
No lesions, no
spurs, no mastis...

310
00:19:23,262 --> 00:19:27,757
Her toes are screwed
up. They're backwards.

311
00:19:27,833 --> 00:19:31,167
<i>You guys know how much surgery
it's gonna take to swap 'em back?</i>

312
00:19:31,237 --> 00:19:33,001
What are you talking about?

313
00:19:33,072 --> 00:19:37,203
Well, either she literally has two
left feet, or you angioed the wrong leg.

314
00:19:44,850 --> 00:19:47,012
That's impossible. It can't
be— Or maybe it was Jenny.

315
00:19:47,086 --> 00:19:48,788
<i>How come some
resident signed this</i>

316
00:19:48,812 --> 00:19:51,046
<i>radiology report? Were
you even in the room?</i>

317
00:19:51,123 --> 00:19:53,183
- I'll redo her angio—
- You'll do nothing!

318
00:19:58,664 --> 00:20:01,224
Foreman, you do the angiogram.

319
00:20:13,546 --> 00:20:15,481
I can't believe I did that.

320
00:20:19,885 --> 00:20:22,878
Why do we have to
redo the angiogram?

321
00:20:22,955 --> 00:20:26,392
There was a shadow on
the first test result. <i>Shadow?</i>

322
00:20:27,693 --> 00:20:29,719
A shadow means there
could be a blood clot, right?

323
00:20:31,397 --> 00:20:34,424
I read <i>Conn's Current Therapy.</i>

324
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:38,301
A real page-turner. No, it
wasn't that kind of shadow.

325
00:20:40,806 --> 00:20:44,106
My chest hurts. <i>It's
from the tracer I injected.</i>

326
00:20:44,176 --> 00:20:49,012
You might also get a little nauseous
