327
00:20:49,081 --> 00:20:52,142
I'm a runner. I
shouldn't feel like this.

328
00:20:52,218 --> 00:20:54,517
Carly, I'm looking at
your vitals right now and...

329
00:20:54,587 --> 00:20:56,579
