330
00:20:58,357 --> 00:20:59,985
My chest.

331
00:21:03,362 --> 00:21:05,297
My chest.

332
00:21:08,734 --> 00:21:10,999
Respiratory arrest. Call code.

333
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:13,301
- What do you got?
- She's drowning.

334
00:21:31,123 --> 00:21:34,093
<i>Foreman did a thoracentesis
