337
00:21:43,803 --> 00:21:45,738
I'm thrilled.

338
00:23:31,744 --> 00:23:33,940
<i>Okay, see, now you’re
just being stubborn.</i>

339
00:23:34,013 --> 00:23:36,676
<i>It's cold. It's a perfectly good
