340
00:23:36,749 --> 00:23:38,684
Carly needs a heart transplant.

341
00:23:40,085 --> 00:23:42,714
Thoracentesis
revealed a transudate?

342
00:23:42,788 --> 00:23:44,950
I haven't gotten it back yet.

343
00:23:45,024 --> 00:23:48,290
Her MUGA scan, what
was the ejection fraction?

344
00:23:48,360 --> 00:23:52,127
<i>Maybe you could treat it
surgically.</i> I haven't done the MUGA.

345
00:23:52,197 --> 00:23:54,496
How do you know she
