346
00:23:55,601 --> 00:23:57,536
I got my aura read today.

347
00:23:57,603 --> 00:24:00,072
It said someone close
to me had a broken heart.

348
00:24:00,139 --> 00:24:02,574
Since when do I need the
secret pass code to talk to you?

349
00:24:02,641 --> 00:24:06,009
I can't tell you anything.
Professional responsibility.

350
00:24:06,078 --> 00:24:08,138
