I'm saying you'd be obligated to.

356
00:24:20,893 --> 00:24:23,328
Because of my
position on the board?

357
00:24:27,466 --> 00:24:29,901
Because of my position on
the transplant committee?

358
00:24:32,338 --> 00:24:35,240
Hey, you brought this up for a
