the way that she looks.

425
00:28:42,321 --> 00:28:44,620
Oh, stop hiding!

426
00:28:44,690 --> 00:28:47,819
<i>I'm asking you if you wanna live
or die? You can't even say that.</i>

427
00:28:47,893 --> 00:28:50,761
What do you want
me to do? Cry? <i>Yes.</i>

428
00:28:50,829 --> 00:28:54,288
I want you to tell me that your life is
important to you, because I don't know.

429
00:28:59,204 --> 00:29:04,438
Because that's what's on
the table right now— your life.

430
00:29:21,159 --> 00:29:23,321
I don't wanna die.

431
00:29:26,698 --> 00:29:28,633
I don't.

432
00:29:36,308 --> 00:29:39,801
<i>This 32-year-old female
